text: Gheorghe Ţarălungă (born 11 February 1941) is a Romanian wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle flyweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Romania Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
